title: Alexandru Suvorov
text: Alexandru Suvorov (born 2 February 1987) is a <a href="Moldova">Moldova</a>n <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er who plays as a <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> for <a href="FC%20Sf%C3%A2ntul%20Gheorghe%20Suruceni">Sfântul Gheorghe</a> and the <a href="Moldova%20national%20football%20team">Moldova national team</a>.
